Company Profile
UPDATES (10)
ASK  QUESTION







“Legion M partners with creators - from independent filmmakers to big Hollywood studios - to bring boldly original new movies, TV shows and virtual reality experiences to market. We're also the first entertainment company in history built from the ground up to be owned by FANS. With the help of the JOBS Act, we're opening the gates of Hollywood and giving fans a first-ever opportunity to go behind the scenes and get in on the ground floor of Hollywood's newest media startup!



Paul Scanlan
CEO, Legion M




Key Facts

Founded by Emmy winning digital media pioneers
SOLD OUT Reg CF seed round was oversubscribed by nearly 30%, with over 3,100 investors--the most in JOBS Act History!
Initial slate of projects includes a feature film starring Anne Hathaway and Jason Sudeikis and a groundbreaking virtual reality series with Stan Lee and Kevin Smith.
Thriving community of over 12,000 members and 5,000 investors
Advisory board of Hollywood heavyweights, including executives from Sony, Legendary/Nerdist/Geek & Sundry, Neon, Alamo Drafthouse, Meltdown, 42 Entertainment, Starlog/Fangoria and more.
Want to see first-hand what Legion M is all about? Join as a free member at: https://thelegionm.com/join

Our Ambition
Legion M is founded on the idea that having a large audience invested in our movie, TV and VR projects will give us a competitive advantage. Our goal is to unite 1 million fans as shareholders of Legion M. This was never possible before the JOBS Act, but if (when!) we achieve this goal, we'll have hundreds of millions of dollars to develop films, TV, and VR projects that have one million fans standing behind them. We believe this could make us one of the most influential companies in Hollywood!
