WILL THE NEXT GREAT MEDIA POWERHOUSE BE OWNED BY...YOU?
Legion M is a new type of company built from the ground up to be owned by fans. For the first time in history, you can join Stan Lee, Kevin Smith, Seth Green, Tim League, Stoopid Buddy Studios, Alamo Drafthouse, Meltdown Comics, 42 Entertainment, and thousands of investors around the world as co-owners of one of the hottest new companies in Hollywood!



GET IN THE ACTION
As a Legion M shareholder, we take you behind the scenes. Whether it's watching live streams from the set or joining our shareholder meetings at Comic-Con, we're opening the gates of Hollywood and bringing you along for the ride!


JOIN THE REVOLUTION

Legion M is a more than just a company, we're a community over 10,000 strong (and growing!). Members get access to local meet-ups, movie openings, online shindigs with creators, member-only forums, and much, much more.


INVEST IN THE FUTURE
Our long-term goal is to unite one million fans as co-owners of Legion M. If we're successful, we could become one of the most influential companies in Hollywood. Join the movement and help us change the world of entertainment for good!



"The idea of setting up a company that will be owned by the fans — I think that is a wonderful idea. So good, I wish I thought of it myself!"



Stan Lee
Former President, Marvel Comics
